<refnamediv id='name'>
<refname>ipsec status</refname>
<refpurpose>asks pluto for current connection status</refpurpose>
</refnamediv>
<!-- body begins here -->
<refsynopsisdiv id='synopsis'>
<cmdsynopsis>
  <command>ipsec</command>
    <arg choice='plain'><replaceable>status [connection name]</replaceable></arg>
</cmdsynopsis>
</refsynopsisdiv>

<refsect1 id='description'><title>DESCRIPTION</title>
<para><emphasis remap='I'>status</emphasis>
is used to ask pluto for current connection status\&. It is the equivalent
to running the commands
<emphasis remap='I'>ipsec whack --status</emphasis>.
</para>
If the connection name is defined then it does the equivalent of:
<emphasis remap='I'>ipsec whack --status | grep -F connection name</emphasis>.
</refsect1>


